@SpringBootApplication 
 - Indicates as Spring Context
 - Enables Auto Configuration
 - Enables Component Scan
 
SpringApplication.run() -> Used to run SpringContext, Returns Application Context

Spring Boot Auto Configuration

Spring Boot Framework checks for Jars present in the class path, based on the jar configurations are done.
Ex: If Spring Web MVC is present, then it configures Dispatcher Servlet, View Resolver etc.




 
